To run the shinyApp you should have R and the shiny package installed. Please download the files on your computer in a new directory and in R type:
library(shiny)
runApp(“path_to_directory_with_files”) 

If you also have RStudio then you can use RStudio to visualise the App:
Please download the files on your computer on a new directory and open the ui.R file with RStudio. Then click "Run App” which is on the top right corner of the ui.R script for the application to run.
